First of all, thanks for the suggestions.

Regarding the TNT and the Uranium: TNT and other conventional explosives can be found in ocean water from unused ordinance that failed to detonate or sank with the ship it was carried on etc., either in their original  or dissolved into the ocean when the casing failed. There are billions of tons of Uranium in the ocean, so much in fact that it is currently possible to retrieve uranium from ocean water, it's just not currently worth it economically. This uranium contains pretty much the same percentage of U-235 as uranium mined normally.

Now that I think about it though, perhaps it might make it better for the protists to synthesize their own high explosives. It is an avenue of research currently being looked into and is possible. I might make a change if more people find it hard to believe.





